<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَمْثَلُهُمْ طَرِيقَةً}</span> ... أَعْلَمُهُمْ، وَأَوْفَاهُمْ عَقْلًا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
