<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نَسْفًا}</span> ... يَجْعَلُهَا هَبَاءً مُنْبَثًّا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
